## Admin portal detail pages

Same `shared/detail/` framework; simpler navigation (no marketplace vs our-listings split).

| Entity | Route | Summary kind | Back link |
|--------|-------|--------------|-----------|
| Users | `users/:id` | `user` (name + email) | `adminHomeUrl('users')` |
| Vehicles | `vehicles/:id` | `vehicle` (make + plate) | `adminHomeUrl('vehicles')` |
| Warehouses | `warehouses/:id` | `warehouse` (name + city) | `adminHomeUrl('warehouses')` |

- Navigation: `portal/admin/common/admin-entity-detail-navigation.ts` — `resolveAdminDetailBack()`, `resolveAdminDetailSubtitleKey()`
- Actions: `buildAdminDetailPageActions()` — always **Edit + Delete** (no send request)
- URLs: `adminUserDetailUrl()`, `adminVehicleDetailUrl()`, `adminWarehouseDetailUrl()` in `admin-urls.ts`
- Row click on hub tables → detail; `viewDetails` row action duplicates row click
- `PageTitleComponent` + `DataTableComponent` use `entityTab`: `users` \| `vehicles` \| `warehouses`
- Detail pages: same `entityTab` on `DetailPageLayoutComponent` — see `entity-service-colors.mdc`
- Delete redirect → `adminHomeUrl(matchingTab)`

Do not reintroduce global detail modal host or sidebar action layout experiments.
